extends layout

block content
	nav.navbar.navbar-expand-md.navbar-light.bg-light
		a.navbar-brand(href='#') Navbar
		button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-toggle='collapse',
				data-target='#navbarTogglerDemo02',
				aria-controls='navbarTogglerDemo02', aria-expanded='false',
				aria-label='Toggle navigation')
			span.navbar-toggler-icon
		#navbarTogglerDemo02.collapse.navbar-collapse
			ul.navbar-nav.mr-auto.mt-2.mt-lg-0
				li.nav-item
					a.nav-link(href='#')
						| Home 
						span.sr-only (current)
				li.nav-item
					a.nav-link(href='#') Link

	section#about.flex.collapse-col
		div.flex.full
			h1 Hey, I'm Sarvesh!
			img(src='../images/headshot.png')
		div.flex.full
			p
				| I was born and raised in the Silicon Valley, and I'm currently
				| pursuing undergraduate degrees in computer science and math at 
				a(href='https://www.utexas.edu/',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') The University of Texas at Austin
				| . Alongside my classes, I'm an Incubator lead at 
				a(href='https://www.txconvergent.org/',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') Texas Convergent 
				| and the Technology Director at the 
				a(href='https://www.texasakpsi.com/',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') Iota chapter 
				| of Alpha Kappa Psi. After graduation, I hope to work at a disruptive
				| technology company.
			p
				| Academically speaking, I'm interested in ___.
				| My main technical skills include ___.
			p
				| In my free time, I enjoy lifting weights, working on side projects, 
				| reading, watching standup comedy, producing music, exploring new 
				| places, and hanging out with friends.

	section#projects.flex.collapse-col
		div.flex.full
			h2 Projects
			a(href='https://github.com/sarveshkalwit'
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank')
				img(src='../images/githublogo.svg')
			div.flex.statistics.f-row
				div
					p 
						span XX
					p public projects
				div
					p 
						span XX
					p contributions in the last year
				div
					p
						span XX
					p all-time contributions
		div.flex.full
			p
				| My favorite part about learning computer science is that it teaches 
				| me how to think critically. It's nephew, software engineering, helps 
				| me build solutions to problems that I face.
			p
				| In general, I enjoy working on projects that will help me, or someone 
				| I can relate to. These have included a 
				a(href='https://github.com/sarveshkalwit/Rate-My-Lift',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') weightlifting form analyzer 
				| which ensures user safety when exercising, a 
				a(href='https://github.com/sarveshkalwit/Supreme-Bot',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') shopping bot 
				| to quickly purchase in-demand clothing items, and a 
				a(href='https://github.com/sarveshkalwit/AKPsi-Website',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') restricted web app 
				| that provides numerous services to the members in my organization.

	section#trading.flex.collapse-col
		div.flex.full
			h2 Trading
			a(href='https://alpaca.markets/'
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank')
				img(src='../images/alpacalogo.png')
			div.flex.statistics.f-row
				.statistic
					p
						span XX
					p trades executed today
				.statistic
					p
						span XX
					p portfolio growth today
				.statistic
					p
						span XX
					p portfolio growth in the last year
		div.flex.full
			p
				| I thoroughly enjoy exploring the intersection between technology 
				| and business. While the allure of getting rich is definitely present, 
				| I was drawn to the stock market, and later cryptocurrencies, more so 
				| by the implicit challenge of making some sense out of something 
				| seemingly nonsensical.
			p
				| I'm currently working on a short term trading bot to identify and 
				| execute on optimal trading opportunities for volatile cryptocurrencies. 
				| I prefer to keep my exact net worth private, but the percentage returns 
				| of my 
				a(href='/',
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank') Alpaca 
				| paper trading account are shown.

	// potential music section

	// potential advice/about section

	// blog section?

	footer.flex.f-row.collapse-col
		div.flex.full.f-row
			a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/sarvesh-kalwit/'
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank')
				img(src='../images/linkedin.svg')
			a(href='https://github.com/sarveshkalwit'
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank')
				img(src='../images/github.svg')
			a(href='https://medium.com/@sarveshkalwit'
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank')
				img(src='../images/medium.svg')
			a(href='https://soundcloud.com/sarvesh_kalwit'
					rel='noopener noreferrer',
					target='_blank')
				img(src='../images/soundcloud.svg')
			// resume
			// email
		div.full
			form.flex
				div.full
					label(for='email') Subscribe and stay updated!
				div.flex.f-row
					input#email.form-control(type='email',
						placeholder='your.email@service.ext')
					button.btn(type='submit') Submit

